Calculating psi50

Figure 4

The equation as written in Table 2:

\[-(3.57 * WD)^{1.73} - 1.09\]

WD <- seq(.2, 1, length.out = 100)
p50 <- -(3.57 * WD ) ^ 1.73 - 1.09
plot(WD, p50)

Proposed edit:

\[-(3.57 * WD^{1.73}) - 1.09\]

WD <- seq(.2, 1, length.out = 100)
p50 <- -(3.57 * WD ^ 1.73)  - 1.09
plot(WD, p50)
